Description: Handle of Rhodian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp.
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.181, 32. Name, Damothemis. A close parallel is Delos TD3680.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0853)
